summary:
After some suggestions from the community, whom wanted to set back the old settings and just disabled my other Plugins, I made this fix. 
It will set your killmove-settings back to vanilla. 

Deactivate/delete the \"...Killmoves only!\".esp and use this one.
descriptionHtml:
After some suggestions from the community, whom wanted to set back the old settings and just disabled my other Plugins, I made this fix. 
It will set your killmove-settings back to vanilla. 

Deactivate/delete the \"...Killmoves only!\".esp and use this one.
After playing with it about an hour, you can delete this plugin.
author: theSoXX
